AIDP Benchmark Toolkit — TPC-DS v4.0.0 Queries
==============================================

These 99 SQL files were generated using the official TPC-DS v4.0.0 tools
(dsqgen) downloaded from https://www.tpc.org and made available under the
TPC EULA included in this directory (EULA.txt).

Generation parameters
---------------------
  Tools version : TPC-DS v4.0.0
  Dialect       : netezza  (closest to Spark SQL syntax)
  Scale factor  : 1 (qualification)
  RNG seed      : 19620718  (canonical qualification seed)
  Mode          : -QUALIFY Y  (deterministic qualification stream — 99 queries
                  in numerical order)

Source command
--------------
  ./tools/dsqgen
    -DIRECTORY query_templates
    -TEMPLATE queryN.tpl                     # looped for N in 1..99
    -DIALECT netezza
    -SCALE 1
    -RNGSEED 19620718
    -QUALIFY Y
    -OUTPUT_DIR /tmp/v4_queries
    -DISTRIBUTIONS ./tools/tpcds.idx

